summary: A simple retext and mix-n-matching of ingame assets to make a new light armor set
descriptionHtml:
Mod title: Nordic Rogue

Date: 24/6/2013

Mod author: BryanWee20

Introduction:
This is my first mod for skyrim, its just a simple retext and mix & match 
of default ingame meshes that makes up both armor sets in this mod.

Summary: 
This mod adds a set of light armor which is craftable at
any forge under the leather category and each piece is fully temperable.
The armor is catered towards thief/assassin type classes. 
Please note that this is a male-only set for the time being.

Installation:
Copy the entire contents into the data folder in main skyrim directory. 
Activate the esp 
Start the game
